  "texts": [
    "We then apply UMAP dimensionality reduction, using the PCA solution as initialization, and the cosine distance as the distance metric.",
    "Clustering was performed via HDBScan to mini-batches of the embeddings, assigning all articles to their nearest event cluster.",
    "Using the dataset-wide vocabulary, we generate a single TF-IDF representation matrix.",
    "After mini-batching, we generate a hierarchical clustering on top of the event-based TF-IDF matrix.",
    "We merge any events with a distance below 0.8 to mitigate the effect of mini-batching, and re-construct the TF-IDF representations."
  ],
